$ NastAero VM8: Portal Frame Under Lateral Load
$ Two columns (vertical, Y-direction) + one beam (horizontal, X-direction)
$ Column height = 4.0m, beam span = 6.0m
$ All CBAR elements, same cross section throughout
$ A=0.01 m^2, I=8.333e-6 m^4, J=1.406e-5 m^4, E=200GPa
$
$ Horizontal force 5000N at top-left corner (node 5) in +X direction
$ Fixed supports at both column bases (nodes 1 and 6)
$
$ Node layout:
$   Left column:  nodes 1-5,  x=0.0, y=0.0 to 4.0 (5 nodes, 4 elements)
$   Right column: nodes 6-10, x=6.0, y=0.0 to 4.0 (5 nodes, 4 elements)
$   Beam:         nodes 5,11,12,13,14,15,10 (shares corner nodes)
$                 x=0.0 to 6.0, y=4.0 (7 nodes, 6 elements)
$
$ Total: 15 unique nodes, 14 CBAR elements
$
$ This is a verification of solver stability for frame structures.
$ Expect lateral sway at top and moment distribution through frame.
$
SOL 101
CEND
TITLE = VM8 - PORTAL FRAME UNDER LATERAL LOAD
SPC = 1
LOAD = 1
DISPLACEMENT(PRINT) = ALL
SPCFORCES(PRINT) = ALL
BEGIN BULK
$
$ Left column nodes: x=0.0, y=0.0 to 4.0
GRID,1,,0.0,0.0,0.0
GRID,2,,0.0,1.0,0.0
GRID,3,,0.0,2.0,0.0
GRID,4,,0.0,3.0,0.0
GRID,5,,0.0,4.0,0.0
$
$ Right column nodes: x=6.0, y=0.0 to 4.0
GRID,6,,6.0,0.0,0.0
GRID,7,,6.0,1.0,0.0
GRID,8,,6.0,2.0,0.0
GRID,9,,6.0,3.0,0.0
GRID,10,,6.0,4.0,0.0
$
$ Beam interior nodes: y=4.0, x=1.0 to 5.0
GRID,11,,1.0,4.0,0.0
GRID,12,,2.0,4.0,0.0
GRID,13,,3.0,4.0,0.0
GRID,14,,4.0,4.0,0.0
GRID,15,,5.0,4.0,0.0
$
$ Left column elements (vertical, v-vector in +Z for XY plane bending)
CBAR,1,1,1,2,0.0,0.0,1.0
CBAR,2,1,2,3,0.0,0.0,1.0
CBAR,3,1,3,4,0.0,0.0,1.0
CBAR,4,1,4,5,0.0,0.0,1.0
$
$ Right column elements (vertical)
CBAR,5,1,6,7,0.0,0.0,1.0
CBAR,6,1,7,8,0.0,0.0,1.0
CBAR,7,1,8,9,0.0,0.0,1.0
CBAR,8,1,9,10,0.0,0.0,1.0
$
$ Beam elements (horizontal, v-vector in +Y for XY plane bending)
CBAR,9,1,5,11,0.0,1.0,0.0
CBAR,10,1,11,12,0.0,1.0,0.0
CBAR,11,1,12,13,0.0,1.0,0.0
CBAR,12,1,13,14,0.0,1.0,0.0
CBAR,13,1,14,15,0.0,1.0,0.0
CBAR,14,1,15,10,0.0,1.0,0.0
$
$ Cross section: 0.1m x 0.1m square
PBAR,1,1,0.01,8.333e-6,8.333e-6,1.406e-5
MAT1,1,200.0e9,,0.3,7850.0
$
$ Fixed supports at column bases
SPC1,1,123456,1
SPC1,1,123456,6
$
$ Horizontal force at top-left corner in +X direction
FORCE,1,5,,5000.0,1.0,0.0,0.0
$
ENDDATA
